gameengine.model

Class PhysicsEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • gameengine.model.PhysicsEngine

  • public class PhysicsEngine
extends java.lang.Object
    Physics Engine Class Handles calculating/assigning new positions based on positional attributes and movement vectors Receives Actor object via movement specific methods (ie moveRight, jump) These methods then apply a set force that affects and updates the Actor's position and velocity variables
    Author:
    justinbergkamp
